Release Title:  Valkaama (Beta)
Release Date:   24 June 2009
Release Length: 01:32:56

Valkaama is a drama set in Sweden and Finland. The movie tells the story of two disparate young men, each seeking his fortune, thrown together by fate to travel to Valkaama. As their paths cross, they do not realize how much of their journey has already been determined by their pasts.
